    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 32-35.</p><p>Song of Legend</p><p>Also at 23rd level, you learn to give a legendary performance that enhances your allies and intimidates your enemies. As an action on your turn, you can play one of the following powerful melodies:</p><ul><li></li></ul><p>Respite: You and up to 10 allies who can hear you within 60 feet gain an amount of temporary hit points equal to five times your Charisma modifier.</p><ul><li></li></ul><p>Tragedy: Creatures of your choice that can hear you within 60 feet must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or become frightened of you until the end of their next turn. A creature that is immune to the frightened condition is Impaired for a minute instead.</p><ul><li></li></ul><p>Valor: You and allies that can hear you within 60 feet gain a +3 to attack and damage rolls until the end of your next turn.</p></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
